Copyrighted scholarly sources (NOT redistributed)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The authority layer cites ~20 in-copyright Egyptological reference works
(Porter & Moss, Leprohon, von Beckerath, Hölbl, Kitchen, Dodson & Hilton,
Ryholt, Shaw, Baud, and others). The works themselves are NOT included in this
repository — the source PDFs live in a separate, private submodule and are never
committed here. Only derived, page-cited factual extracts are present. See
docs/playbook-phase-0-ocr-transcription.md ("Rights policy") for the project's
documented sourcing and rights approach.
